

### PRODUCTION ###
GET https://mcp-hello-node.onrender.com/healthz



### Statless tool call (the only one you need)
POST https://mcp-hello-node.onrender.com/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "1",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "greet",
    "arguments": { "name": "Chris" }
  }
}



### DEVELOPMENT ###

### Call fetch_external_data via MCP (JSON-RPC)
POST http://localhost:8000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "1",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "fetch_external_data",
    "arguments": {}
  }
}

### Call greet (stateless)
POST http://localhost:8000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "1",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "greet",
    "arguments": { "name": "Chris" }
  }
}

### GET /mcp (should be 405 in stateless)
GET http://localhost:8000/mcp
Accept: text/event-stream

### DELETE /mcp (should be 405 in stateless)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/mcp
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream
